name: AlphaExchangeAI
description: AlphaExchanges AI is a decentralized quantitative trading platform that combines AI and blockchain technology, providing users with a secure, transparent, and intelligent global quantitative financial ecosystem through AI intelligent strategies, on chain transparent settlement, and non custodial fund models. As the core driving force of the platform, AEA tokens achieve profit driven consumption and destruction through a fuel mechanism, forming a long-term value loop.
